@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
    Layout = "~/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>
        This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and protect your personal data when using our reporting platform.
        By submitting reports, uploading photos, or interacting with the system, you agree to the practices described below.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🔐 What Data We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Your name and email address (if provided during registration or authentication)</li>
        <li>Submitted reports and descriptions</li>
        <li>Uploaded photos related to reports</li>
        <li>IP address and device information for security purposes</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🛡️ How We Use Your Data</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To allow you to create, manage, and track reports</li>
        <li>To enable administrators to respond to your reports appropriately</li>
        <li>To generate statistics that help improve public services</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 class="mt-4">📸 Photo Privacy</h4>
    <p>
        All uploaded photos are publicly visible if the report is accepted. Do not upload images containing sensitive personal information.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">🗑️ Data Retention & Deletion</h4>
    <p>
        Reports and associated data are stored securely and may be retained for audit and transparency purposes. If you want your data removed,
        you may contact the system administrator using the contact form provided.
    </p>

    <h4 class="mt-4">📬 Contact</h4>
    <p>
        If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please email us at <a href="mailto:support@rezolvam.local">support@rezolvam.local</a>.
    </p>
</div>
